dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T09:37:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你暪我暪<br />\ni miss you<br />\n沒有你我甚麼都不是</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nI miss you對陳柏宇黎講係唔錯，<br />\n但後來既你瞞我瞞佢話左比我地聽佢係可以做到更多，所以I miss you可foul，有更多選擇"},{"pid":"2e894abff758e2e333463a84e5a75f883c6c7213","tid":430871,"uid":5866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T09:40:39.000Z","msg":"I will be loving you<br />\n遲愛<br />\n我沒有"},{"pid":"42534f27d4e378aa873f71c84f8b70dcf243d91e","tid":430871,"uid":127196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T12:50:15.000Z","msg":"尊嚴<br />\n你瞞我瞞<br />\n斷絕來往"},{"pid":"bcce46f5cf29de89fb7635a24380cd3e65f8df3e","tid":430871,"uid":141892,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T13:09:34.000Z","msg":"no1  多此一愛"},{"pid":"d5b8d0be63e45bfaa6fc150356c1768546617dff","tid":430871,"uid":67289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T15:18:31.000Z","msg":"木馬小盒<br />\n固執<br />\n親愛的仇人"},{"pid":"6f9f59907ff555e32236c4363e1906501124ad09","tid":430871,"uid":23414,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T15:24:40.000Z","msg":"告別之前<br />\n巴別塔<br />\n車匙<br />\n其實拍乳所有歌都top"},{"pid":"897744275855c2e069d967172383f981456504e2","tid":430871,"uid":2265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T15:45:52.000Z","msg":"時機<br />\n你暪我暪<br />\n沒有你，我甚麼都不是"},{"pid":"7adff265bb23616c6a14d55c5f38a423870d170d","tid":430871,"uid":48604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T02:42:56.000Z","msg":"非常難揀 最後揀左呢3首<br />\n斷絕來往<br />\n永久保存<br />\n車匙"},{"pid":"e987c64fb22aef422d16a2bf9bb953cb9772c6d3","tid":430871,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T02:59:26.000Z","msg":"斷絕來往<br />\n你暪我暪<br />\n沒有吻的資格<br />\n<br />\n別來無恙 啲詞寫得唔好"},{"pid":"c3324348ab076c3a8602b479fb36350a0f802af0","tid":430871,"uid":67509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T03:04:18.000Z","msg":"Mr. Adult <br />\n繭<br />\n黑馬王子"},{"pid":"581ea1442db28e25b6ab6ae65ce4704c37460e07","tid":430871,"uid":67509,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T03:10:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>斷絕來往<br />\n你暪我暪<br />\n沒有吻的資格<br />\n<br />\n別來無恙 啲詞寫得唔好</blockquote><br />\n別來無恙先係神詞，醉酒佬自言自語，去到「現在剩我一個」之後情緒大爆發，成首歌講到自己已經Move on，但最尾情緒爆發完都係「恨不得當初，懂得愛惜你」<br />\n一個平時唔入廚房嘅男人要悶到點、孤獨到點先會肯自己做飯，成首根本sad到極點"},{"pid":"a4353c9454560716705801341001313353ffa822","tid":430871,"uid":92800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T03:17:37.000Z","msg":"你瞞我瞞<br />\n回眸一笑<br />\n拍一半拖<br />\n<br />\n其他都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf08b1f33ab61d9bd979beaf96aae6d616365944","tid":430871,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T03:32:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>斷絕來往<br />\n你暪我暪<br />\n沒有吻的資格<br />\n<br />\n別來無恙 啲詞寫得唔好</blockquote><br />\n別來無恙先係神詞，醉酒佬自言自語，去到「現在剩我一個」之後情緒大爆發，成首歌講到自己已經Move on，但最尾情緒爆發完都係「恨不得當初，懂得愛惜你」<br />\n一個平時唔入廚房嘅男人要悶到點、孤獨到點先會肯自己做飯，成首根本sad到極點</blockquote><br />\n佢主線好但用字差<br />\nanyway 各有睇法，但呢首我都係會成日聽既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個MV好好睇"},{"pid":"aa26472c1729e5c6e4b5e812f87f12c30db61dc6","tid":430871,"uid":146287,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T03:32:53.000Z","msg":"別來無恙<br />\n告別之前<br />\n斷絕來往"},{"pid":"d8bcb02221165b4bafdc60694f6b9157eafc7f16","tid":430871,"uid":65780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T03:35:25.000Z","msg":"買咗飛等入埸聽speechless<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9111e732d51e145b167104af5736c926d5da528b","tid":430871,"uid":23135,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T03:35:38.000Z","msg":"逸後<br />\n別來無恙<br />\n<br />\n第三隻容我揀隻冷門小小<br />\n<br />\n時機<br />\n<br />\n糖兄（無錯，攞糖妹底褲劣鳩果個）作曲填詞一手包辦<br />\n<br />\n直頭好似講緊佢自己咁"},{"pid":"bfb3a7cbdb097b